INSERT INTO `cr_car_reviews` VALUES (1,'Outstanding rental experience! Premium sound system was amazing The car was like driving a brand new car and handled like a dream on every road. The team was absolutely wonderful to work with Exceeded all expectations. Will definitely be back!',5,21,16,NULL,'published','2025-04-22 15:08:42','2025-11-27 20:09:01'),(2,'Average rental experience. It was a standard rental car experience Minor scuff on the bumper but the price was fair. Nothing special but gets the job done.',3,26,51,NULL,'published','2025-06-30 14:59:04','2025-11-27 20:09:01'),(3,'Decent car for the price. The air conditioning was effective one cup holder being a bit loose but overall acceptable for weekend getaway. Would consider again if needed.',3,18,19,NULL,'published','2024-06-25 06:40:19','2025-11-27 20:09:01'),(4,'Best rental car I\'ve ever had! The quality was absolutely pristine Outstanding professionalism and care Premium experience at a fair price Everything was perfect from start to finish. Will definitely use again!',5,26,25,NULL,'published','2025-06-15 01:27:51','2025-11-27 20:09:01'),(5,'Perfect car for our weekend getaway! Exceptional ergonomics and support Exceptional driving dynamics in all conditions Outstanding professionalism and care Cannot fault anything about this rental. 10/10 would recommend!',5,32,96,NULL,'published','2024-01-27 19:40:19','2025-11-27 20:09:01'),(6,'Standard rental car. No major issues during our rental The pickup process took a while Meets expectations without exceeding them Met basic expectations.',3,30,21,NULL,'published','2024-06-05 23:51:32','2025-11-27 20:09:01'),(7,'Absolutely fantastic! The technology was cutting-edge and intuitive Not a single issue throughout our entire rental Everything about this rental was perfect This is how car rentals should be done. Thank you for an amazing experience!',5,14,9,NULL,'published','2025-07-10 23:43:19','2025-11-27 20:09:01'),(8,'Great rental experience! Very comfortable seats The car was clean and well-maintained and was surprisingly quiet and smooth. Could use a bit more trunk space but overall very satisfied. Would definitely rent again.',4,6,65,NULL,'published','2024-07-14 14:03:06','2025-11-27 20:09:01'),(9,'Outstanding rental experience! The most comfortable seats I\'ve experienced The car was absolutely pristine and was remarkably quiet and refined. The staff went above and beyond to help us Exceeded all expectations. Will definitely be back!',5,7,8,NULL,'published','2024-08-09 06:26:14','2025-11-27 20:09:01'),(10,'Great rental experience! Excellent fuel economy The car was clean and well-maintained and was surprisingly quiet and smooth. The GPS was a bit outdated but overall very satisfied. Would definitely rent again.',4,2,78,NULL,'published','2024-11-18 12:08:28','2025-11-27 20:09:01'),(11,'Below expectations. Could use a bit more trunk space The car was satisfactory for short trips but The cleanliness standards. The pickup process was smooth but overall not satisfied with the rental.',2,1,28,NULL,'published','2024-04-20 19:03:08','2025-11-27 20:09:01'),(12,'Absolutely fantastic! Advanced capabilities that impressed everyone Zero problems - just pure dependability This rental exceeded every expectation This is how car rentals should be done. Thank you for an amazing experience!',5,13,100,NULL,'published','2025-08-26 02:12:17','2025-11-27 20:09:01'),(13,'Excellent value for money. Excellent safety features gave us confidence No unexpected problems or breakdowns Contributed to a memorable road trip Will book with them again for sure.',4,26,78,NULL,'published','2023-12-20 01:42:44','2025-11-27 20:09:01'),(14,'Outstanding rental experience! Whisper-quiet cabin and smooth ride The car was like driving a brand new car and exceeded all performance expectations. Outstanding customer service from start to finish Exceeded all expectations. Will definitely be back!',5,23,17,NULL,'published','2024-11-28 15:47:52','2025-11-27 20:09:01'),(15,'Outstanding rental experience! Whisper-quiet cabin and smooth ride The car was immaculate in every detail and exceeded all performance expectations. The team was absolutely wonderful to work with Exceeded all expectations. Will definitely be back!',5,16,39,NULL,'published','2024-03-16 16:03:45','2025-11-27 20:09:01'),(16,'Average rental experience. Average car for an average price Minor scuff on the bumper but the pickup was convenient. Nothing special but gets the job done.',3,23,26,NULL,'published','2025-03-24 13:30:06','2025-11-27 20:09:01'),(17,'Decent car for the price. The handling was predictable the radio taking a moment to connect to Bluetooth but overall acceptable for vacation. Would consider again if needed.',3,14,57,NULL,'published','2025-01-29 13:52:08','2025-11-27 20:09:01'),(18,'Excellent value for money. Great visibility from all angles Never had a single mechanical issue Enhanced our weekend getaway experience Will book with them again for sure.',4,15,34,NULL,'published','2024-01-11 01:10:48','2025-11-27 20:09:01'),(19,'Had some issues with this rental. The air conditioning was barely working making the trip uncomfortable in hot weather The price was reasonable but the quality didn\'t match.',2,18,64,NULL,'published','2024-03-11 01:50:22','2025-11-27 20:09:01'),(20,'Outstanding rental experience! Whisper-quiet cabin and smooth ride The car was showroom quality and was remarkably quiet and refined. Outstanding customer service from start to finish Exceeded all expectations. Will definitely be back!',5,32,47,NULL,'published','2024-01-13 19:37:28','2025-11-27 20:09:01'),(21,'Outstanding rental experience! Surprisingly spacious for our family The car was immaculate in every detail and delivered outstanding fuel economy. Outstanding customer service from start to finish Exceeded all expectations. Will definitely be back!',5,28,40,NULL,'published','2025-05-09 11:15:39','2025-11-27 20:09:01'),(22,'Absolutely fantastic! The technology was cutting-edge and intuitive Zero problems - just pure dependability The best rental car experience we\'ve ever had This is how car rentals should be done. Thank you for an amazing experience!',5,15,86,NULL,'published','2025-04-30 10:49:53','2025-11-27 20:09:01'),(23,'Very pleased with this rental. Attention to detail was evident throughout Quick and easy pickup process Excellent option for families Just a small issue with the owner\'s manual being missing but nothing major.',4,24,37,NULL,'published','2024-07-28 11:22:13','2025-11-27 20:09:01'),(24,'Great rental experience! Excellent fuel economy The car was very reliable and had plenty of power when needed. The pickup process took a while but overall very satisfied. Would definitely rent again.',4,7,24,NULL,'published','2024-02-18 23:25:34','2025-11-27 20:09:01'),(25,'Very pleased with this rental. Well-maintained and cared for vehicle Quick and easy pickup process Excellent option for families Just a small issue with the pickup location being slightly hard to find but nothing major.',4,26,22,NULL,'published','2024-08-05 18:39:53','2025-11-27 20:09:01'),(26,'Best rental car I\'ve ever had! The quality was absolutely pristine The customer service was world-class Outstanding value for the price paid Everything was perfect from start to finish. Will definitely use again!',5,3,90,NULL,'published','2024-02-07 23:05:30','2025-11-27 20:09:01'),(27,'Excellent value for money. Great visibility from all angles Started every time without hesitation Contributed to a memorable road trip Will book with them again for sure.',4,15,72,NULL,'published','2024-10-02 17:19:15','2025-11-27 20:09:01'),(28,'Absolutely fantastic! The technology was cutting-edge and intuitive Performed flawlessly under all conditions The best rental car experience we\'ve ever had This is how car rentals should be done. Thank you for an amazing experience!',5,20,64,NULL,'published','2025-01-24 21:23:36','2025-11-27 20:09:01'),(29,'Excellent value for money. The automatic climate control worked perfectly Completely dependable for our entire trip Contributed to a memorable road trip Will book with them again for sure.',4,26,40,NULL,'published','2024-08-12 12:46:30','2025-11-27 20:09:01'),(30,'Decent car for the price. The visibility was good the radio taking a moment to connect to Bluetooth but overall acceptable for business trip. Would consider again if needed.',3,30,26,NULL,'published','2023-12-09 08:04:34','2025-11-27 20:09:01'),(31,'Mixed feelings about this rental. the overall condition was satisfactory but the customer service could be improved. Standard rental experience Fair value for money.',3,22,35,NULL,'published','2024-12-04 23:18:31','2025-11-27 20:09:01'),(32,'Disappointing rental experience. The communication with staff was problematic and The engine was making strange noises. Some good points but too many negatives.',2,32,93,NULL,'published','2024-09-12 10:00:01','2025-11-27 20:09:01'),(33,'Excellent value for money. Great visibility from all angles Performed consistently throughout our rental Made our vacation stress-free and enjoyable Will book with them again for sure.',4,3,40,NULL,'published','2025-06-30 20:45:48','2025-11-27 20:09:01'),(34,'Disappointing rental experience. The vehicle\'s mechanical condition was problematic and The interior was dirty and smelled bad. Some good points but too many negatives.',2,7,96,NULL,'published','2024-08-20 09:37:47','2025-11-27 20:09:01'),(35,'Absolutely fantastic! Premium features that enhanced every moment Reliability that exceeded all expectations Everything about this rental was perfect This is how car rentals should be done. Thank you for an amazing experience!',5,10,95,NULL,'published','2025-08-01 21:32:33','2025-11-27 20:09:01'),(36,'Absolutely fantastic! Every feature worked flawlessly Not a single issue throughout our entire rental A truly exceptional experience from start to finish This is how car rentals should be done. Thank you for an amazing experience!',5,9,41,NULL,'published','2024-03-20 05:21:21','2025-11-27 20:09:01'),(37,'Really enjoyed driving this car. Climate control worked perfectly Reliable performance throughout our trip Perfect for our family vacation Only minor complaint is the cup holders were a bit small. Highly recommend!',4,29,43,NULL,'published','2024-12-14 07:29:14','2025-11-27 20:09:01'),(38,'Great rental experience! Smooth and quiet ride The car was clean and well-maintained and had plenty of power when needed. The GPS was a bit outdated but overall very satisfied. Would definitely rent again.',4,10,3,NULL,'published','2025-02-20 10:10:49','2025-11-27 20:09:01'),(39,'Terrible experience with this car. The air conditioning wasn\'t working properly The vehicle was in poor condition and felt unsafe to drive. Would not recommend to anyone. Customer service was unhelpful when I reported the issues.',1,20,14,NULL,'published','2025-08-12 16:31:54','2025-11-27 20:09:01'),(40,'Below expectations. Could use a bit more trunk space The car was adequate for the price point but The pickup/return process. The staff was friendly enough but overall not satisfied with the rental.',2,28,10,NULL,'published','2023-12-05 22:08:13','2025-11-27 20:09:01'),(41,'Perfect car for our weekend getaway! Every passenger commented on the amazing comfort Performance that rivals much more expensive cars Service that sets the gold standard Cannot fault anything about this rental. 10/10 would recommend!',5,16,51,NULL,'published','2025-07-23 08:24:53','2025-11-27 20:09:01'),(42,'Very disappointed. The maintenance was clearly lacking The engine was completely worn out and warning lights were on. Not worth the money at all.',1,31,82,NULL,'published','2024-10-22 16:39:11','2025-11-27 20:09:01'),(43,'Perfect car for our business trip! Exceptional ergonomics and support Incredible power delivery and smooth operation Service that sets the gold standard Cannot fault anything about this rental. 10/10 would recommend!',5,29,58,NULL,'published','2024-12-10 12:03:33','2025-11-27 20:09:01'),(44,'Average rental experience. Average car for an average price The pickup process took a while but the price was fair. Nothing special but gets the job done.',3,7,74,NULL,'published','2024-08-13 00:19:23','2025-11-27 20:09:01'),(45,'Below expectations. The radio presets weren\'t cleared The car was decent enough for basic needs but The vehicle\'s mechanical condition. The staff was friendly enough but overall not satisfied with the rental.',2,20,83,NULL,'published','2025-04-24 11:32:16','2025-11-27 20:09:01'),(46,'Really enjoyed driving this car. Very quiet cabin for conversations Good handling in various driving conditions Made our trip so much more enjoyable Only minor complaint is the pickup location was hard to find. Highly recommend!',4,10,5,NULL,'published','2025-06-30 18:53:59','2025-11-27 20:09:01'),(47,'Excellent value for money. The infotainment system was user-friendly Performed consistently throughout our rental Perfect companion for our business travel Will book with them again for sure.',4,11,7,NULL,'published','2024-03-13 01:41:35','2025-11-27 20:09:01'),(48,'Great rental experience! Easy to drive and park The car was spotless inside and out and was very fuel efficient. Minor scuff on the bumper but overall very satisfied. Would definitely rent again.',4,31,95,NULL,'published','2025-06-30 21:13:53','2025-11-27 20:09:01'),(49,'Really enjoyed driving this car. Very quiet cabin for conversations The car felt stable and well-balanced Great for city driving and parking Only minor complaint is one of the USB ports wasn\'t working. Highly recommend!',4,19,29,NULL,'published','2024-11-20 10:54:43','2025-11-27 20:09:01'),(50,'Outstanding rental experience! Surprisingly spacious for our family The car was showroom quality and handled like a dream on every road. Incredibly professional and courteous service Exceeded all expectations. Will definitely be back!',5,13,59,NULL,'published','2025-01-22 10:02:14','2025-11-27 20:09:01'),(51,'Perfect car for our conference! Exceptional ergonomics and support Exceptional driving dynamics in all conditions Outstanding professionalism and care Cannot fault anything about this rental. 10/10 would recommend!',5,14,14,NULL,'published','2025-06-08 03:07:24','2025-11-27 20:09:01'),(52,'Excellent value for money. The automatic climate control worked perfectly No unexpected problems or breakdowns Reliable transportation for our family trip Will book with them again for sure.',4,17,54,NULL,'published','2024-02-02 10:47:22','2025-11-27 20:09:01');
/*!40000 ALTER TABLE `cr_car_reviews` ENABLE KEYS */;
